Title: A monte-carlo approach to the VaR (Value at Risk)
Slug: monte-carlo-var
Date: 2019-05-11 14:10
Category: Finance
Tags:
Author: Tiwx2
Description: The VaR is a usefull technique for quantifying risk. Although the theory is quite straight forward, the application migh prove a bit tricky. In this article, you will find one approach to implementing the VaR using Python. A special emphasis has been placed on the problem of taking correlation into account when implementing the method.